snippet: Álvaro Negredo and Edin Dzeko scored two goals each and Sergio Agüero scored on his return from injury as Manchester City swept to a 5-0 win over Blackburn in an English F.A. Cup third-round replay.
abstract: Manchester City sweeps Blackburn, 5-0, in third round of the English FA Cup; other soccer news noted.

byline.original: By THE ASSOCIATED PRESS and JACK BELL

lead_paragraph: Álvaro Negredo and Edin Dzeko scored two goals each and Sergio Agüero scored on his return from injury as Manchester City swept to a 5-0 win over Blackburn in an English F.A. Cup third-round replay.

headline.main: Manchester City Cruises in F.A. Cup
headline.print_headline: Manchester City Cruises in F.A. Cup
